"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Áp suất:</strong> 3 - 5 bar</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Lưu lượng:</strong> 7 - 16m3/h</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Đường kính họng phun: </strong>14, 16, 18, 20mm</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Chiều dài họng phun:</strong> 4.5mm</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Tốc độ vòng quay:</strong> 60s.</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Chân ren gắn ống:</strong> Ren trong 60mm</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Độ bền:</strong> &gt;5 năm.</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Thân súng tưới cây:</strong> Hợp kim nhôm cao cấp</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Cốt  (lõi bên trong):</strong> Đồng 100%</span></span></span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px; outline:0px; list-style:none; border:0px none\"/>\n<span style=\"border:0px none; box-sizing:border-box; padding:0px\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"list-style:none\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold\">Máy bơm phù hợp:</strong> Đất không đồi dốc. bơm điện 3HP - 5HP phun 1 cái: 23 - 25m. Bơm dầu D12 phun 1 cái. Mỗi cái 27m. Bơm càng lớn phun càng xa. Đất có đồi dốc: bơm dầu D18 - 28 phun từ 4 cây bán kính phun: &gt;27m.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"color:#777777\"><span style=\"fon