-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Tiết kiệm tối đa nguồn điện</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Dòng nước đi qua với lưu lượng lớn</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Dễ dàng vệ sinh và làm sạch</span></span></li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379.jpg?v=1603092905 600w, https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379-300x163.jpg?v=1603092905 300w, https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379-150x81.jpg?v=1603092905 150w, https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379-510x276.jpg?v=1603092905 510w\" height=\"325\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" src=\"https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379.jpg\" srcset=\"https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379.jpg?v=1603092905 600w, https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379-300x163.jpg?v=1603092905 300w, https://i-green.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/van-dien-tu-tuoi-tu-dong-baccara-israel-phi-60mm23-e1603092932379-150x81.jpg?v=1603092