-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\'font-family:\"Open Sans\"\'><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><b style=\'box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold; color:#000000; font-family:\"Open Sans\"; font-size:13px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\'><span data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';\" style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"line-height:21.4667px\"><span style=\'font-family:\"Times New Roman\", serif\'>Điểm nổi bật của béc tưới BB 991 là tính đơn giản, góc quay 360 độ linh động, đường kính tưới tương đối rộng 4-5m</span></span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0px 0px 9px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 1px 1px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"display:block\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\'font-family:\"Open Sans\"\'><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><b style=\'box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:bold; color:#000000; font-family:\"Open Sans\"; font-size:13px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\'><span data-mce-style=\"f